headline: Lam Research (LRCX) Is Up 19.1% After Analysts Spotlight Its AI-Focused Chipmaking Tools
summary: In recent days, Lam Research has attracted heightened attention after multiple research firms, including Citi and Aletheia Capital, highlighted the company’s strong position in semiconductor equipment tied to artificial intelligence and high-performance computing demand.
